=====================================================================================

In some cases (umask settings!), the current user does not create with group
write permissions. When, on the other hand, the current user is different from
the developer (ej chroot setups / container user), the developer will not be 
able to start coding without adapting permissions, even though he has carefully 
crafted the groups outside and inside the chroot / container environment and is 
part of the gid of the current user.

